title: NYC's Lyubov Denisova is women's Detroit marathon winner
text:
Published By: Detroit Free Press - Today 
Lyubov Denisova, 44, of New York City is the women's winner of the 38th Detroit Free Press/Talmer Bank Marathon. ...
